# EriDiffusion-v2 — Navigation Map

Pure-Rust trainers. Sister to `flame-core` (tensor + autograd) and
`inference-flame` (inference). Read this first after `/clear` to orient.

Workspace at `/home/alex/EriDiffusion/EriDiffusion-v2/`. Two crates:

| Crate | Path | Role |
|---|---|---|
| `eridiffusion-core` | `crates/eridiffusion-core/` | library: models, training loop, encoders, samplers, data, LoRA/LyCORIS, offload |
| `eridiffusion-cli` | `crates/eridiffusion-cli/` | binaries: `train_*`, `prepare_*`, `sample_*`, `parity_*` |

`flame-core` is pinned at `=26.15.1` in workspace `Cargo.toml` — flame-core
minor bumps are an ABI gate, EDv2 follows in lockstep.

## 1. Binaries (60 total in `crates/eridiffusion-cli/src/bin/`)

Run from workspace root: `cargo run --release --bin <name> -- <config.toml>`.

| Family | Count | Pattern |
|---|---|---|
| `train_*` | 17 | the trainers — read these first when porting/debugging |
| `prepare_*` | 14 | dataset prep: encode captions + VAE latents to cache |
| `sample_*` | 13 | render samples mid-/post-training from a checkpoint |
| `parity_*` | 12 | per-model PyTorch-vs-flame parity harnesses |
| `convert_*` | 1 | LoRA format converters (e.g. `convert_zimage_lora`) |
| misc | 3 | `bench_linear_parity`, `decode_cached_anima`, `vae_bisect` |

Trainers shipped (17 `train_*.rs` binaries): `acestep`, `anima`, `asymflow`,
`chroma`, `ernie`, `flux`, `hidream_o1`, `klein` (4B/9B), `l2p`, `ltx2`,
`qwenimage`, `sd35`, `sdxl`, `slider_klein`, `u1` (SenseNova), `wan22`,
`zimage`. The `models/` table below lists shared per-model module files;
some trainer binaries (e.g. `train_hidream_o1`, `train_l2p`,
`train_slider_klein`) live as binaries only and reuse other models'
core modules.

**Configs live FLAT under `configs/*.json`** — e.g. `configs/klein9b_alina.json`,
`configs/eri2_chroma_lora.json`, `configs/asymflux2_klein_lora.json`.
No per-model subdirectories. `ls configs/` to find yours. Always grep
configs before assuming defaults — many trainer-specific flags only
appear there.

## 2. `eridiffusion-core/src/` layout

```
adapter.rs               trait Adapter (LoRA-like injection points)
config/                  TrainConfig, enums (optimizer, scheduler, etc.)
data/                    bucket_dataset.rs (multi-resolution bucketing)
debug.rs
encoders/                CLIP-L/G, T5-XXL, UMT5, Llama3, Mistral3B, Qwen2.5VL/Qwen3,
                         Gemma3, plus every VAE (flux/sdxl/ltx2/wan21/wan22/zimage/ldm)
lib.rs                   re-exports flame_core, defines EriDiffusionError
lora.rs                  LoRALinear primitive (project-owned, not lycoris-rs)
lycoris.rs               LyCORIS adapter glue (LoCon / LoHa / LoKr / OFT — via eri-lycoris)
models/                  per-model TrainableModel impls (see below)
pipeline/                TrainingPipeline trait (prepare_inputs + compute_loss)
sampler/                 per-model sampling for mid-training preview
training/                training loop + features (see below)
utils/
video/                   video-specific helpers (ltx2 / wan22)
```

